HEADWORD: Mtier
<hw>M⟦eacute⟧`tier"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>Calling; vocation; business; trade.</def></p>

<p><q>Not only is it the business of no one to preach the truth but it
is the <qex>m⟦eacute⟧tier</qex> of many to conceal it.</q> <rj><qau>A.
